<p>Attach concept tags to exercises to track student knowledge of each concept covered in class.</p>

<em>Step 1: Create concept tag.</em>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to <strong>Learning Plan > Concepts</strong>.</li>
    <li>Click <strong>New Concept</strong>.</li>
    <li>Enter concept name and click <strong>Create Concept</strong>.</li>
  </ol>
<em>Step 2: Attach concept tag to an exercise.</em>
  <ol>
    <li>Return to the <strong>Topics section</strong>.</li>
    <li>Create a new exercise, or edit an existing exercise.</li>
    <li>Select the concept tag from the dropdown Concept menu.</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Update Topic Exercise</strong>. Your exercise is now tagged.</li>
</ol>
